while doing my homework.

179
00:12:43,530 --> 00:12:48,040
I guess there's no point
in doing it in my dreams. Right?

180
00:12:48,710 --> 00:12:51,340
Homework?

181
00:12:53,648 --> 00:13:00,170
You studied with me so much
that now you're dreaming of it, High School Girl?

182
00:13:00,170 --> 00:13:02,820
<i>It's creepy how he's just like his current self.</i>

183
00:13:02,820 --> 00:13:04,130
What's with the face?

184
00:13:04,130 --> 00:13:06,060
It's nothing.

185
00:13:07,470 --> 00:13:13,635
Anyway, you're studying in a dream?
You're such a good student.

186
00:13:14,230 --> 00:13:16,140
Mr. Haiba.

187
00:13:19,380 --> 00:13:21,080
Mr...

188
00:13:23,780 --> 00:13:28,140
You're studying too, right?

189
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:35,720
No, I'm writing a diary. Kind of like a will.

190
00:13:39,890 --> 00:13:41,700
Mr. Haiba.

191
00:13:42,395 --> 00:13:44,824
<i>I don't belong here.</i>

192
00:13:44,824 --> 00:13:51,864
<i>But I probably don't belong anywhere
in this entire world.</i>

193
00:13:51,864 --> 00:13:56,300
<i>I shouldn't exist in this world.</i>

194
00:14:02,380 --> 00:14:04,830
