But still, that would fit the mood here perfectly.

294
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:52,995
Sparklers, I mean.

295
00:20:52,995 --> 00:20:55,645
But even those...

296
00:20:57,525 --> 00:21:00,630
Oh, incense is nice too.

297
00:21:00,630 --> 00:21:03,190
We can just look at them.

298
00:21:03,190 --> 00:21:07,430
These summer memories will stay with us.

299
00:21:07,430 --> 00:21:10,300
